 *
 * MESSAGE:	MSG_FFD_LOAD_CURRENT_RECORD_TO_SCREEN for
 *	    	    FlatFileDatabaseClass
 *
 * DESCRIPTION:	This method loads the TEMP_DATA_ROW with field info from
 *	    	the current record, then loads the current layout's screen
